text: Shahriar Komol (born 6 July 1995) is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He made his List A debut for Khelaghar Samaj Kallyan Samity in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Cricket League on 1 April 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Khelaghar Samaj Kallyan Samity cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
